scene.message:
???: Oh, hello. Nice to meet{nl}
you.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm Mariko Yabe, of the{nl}
Yamagumo Private High School{nl}
Paranormal Phenomena Club.{waitkey}Pleased to meet you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Though it's an unofficial club{nl}
where I'm both president and{nl}
sole member, ha!{waitkey}{clearbox}My homeroom teacher won't{nl}
approve the club, for the sole{nl}
reason that it's "uncool"!{waitkey}{clearbox}So today I came to meet my{nl}
comrade Kuroori, but...

{nl}
{nl}
little did I{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
little did I{wait_fr:30}...

{nl}
dream...{waitkey}{clearbox}that I'd get caught up in a{nl}
paranormal event this amazing!{nl}
I'm super lucky!{waitkey}{clearbox}I've been snapping tons of{nl}
photos! And I'm gonna submit{nl}
these demon photos to a{nl}
magazine!{waitkey}{clearbox}Then! Maybe my teacher will{nl}
approve the club after all!{waitkey}All right! I'll give it{nl}
my all!{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: I'm thinking of{nl}
interviewing a demon, but{waitkey}{clearbox}I haven't got a tape recorder{nl}
or a mic. Say, do you think{nl}
they're sold{waitkey}somewhere?{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Welcome~ Me come{nl}
from Demon Mountain. Me bring{nl}
very good things~{waitkey}

Mister, you need this. Me{nl}
give good price. You buy,{nl}
yes!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: At this level, even{nl}
the goods on sale come pretty{nl}
dear.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: That seller's clothes{nl}
are cute! Ayase wants them{nl}
too!{waitkey}{ret}
